Package: cmapr
Title: Tools for Career Mobility Analysis with the CMap Dataset
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Alex", "Farach", email = "alexfarach@microsoft.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    Provides tidy tools for analyzing the CMap Career Mobility Dataset, the largest open dataset of global job transitions.
    Includes functions to download, load, and explore career transition networks, job title mappings, sector specialization, and promotion pathways.
    Designed for efficient and reproducible research using the tidyverse ecosystem.
    See <https://farach.github.io/cmapr> for documentation and usage examples.
